Bob Boozer
siwkay niza tatama ciniza, nalecuhan i Omaha, Nebraska, nanu syubay kanas-mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput. Bob Boozer i 1959 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 1 ku uwac atu silsil 1, namapili' tu nu Cincinnati Royals putiput. 4 bulad 26 demiad, 1937 a mihca, Bob Boozer, miunduay. (mapatay i 2012 a mihca)
